Alfredo
=======

- 1/4 cup butter
- 1c cream
- garlic
- 1.5 cups parmesan grated


melt butter on medium lo flame, add garlic and simmer until browned.
turn heat off, add cream, stir to combine and return to low flame
add 1.5 cups grated parmesan cheese slowly until sauce forms
salt to taste, serve warm
